The '''19,016th Imperial Line Infantry (Training) Company''' was the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] training [[Company/Legends|company]] stationed at [[Training Camp IMIIF-138]] on [[Sirpar/Legends|Sirpar]]. Nearly the size of a [[Battalion/Legends|battalion]], the company consisted of six [[Line platoon|infantry platoons]] and two [[Assault platoon|heavy-weapons platoons]]. Each [[Platoon/Legends|platoon]] consisted of eight [[Squad/Legends|squads]], each of which had eight trainees who were commanded by a training [[Sergeant/Legends|sergeant]].

This meant that the [[line company]] and each individual platoon was [[Imperial Army/Legends#Augmentation|augmented]].<ref name="ISB2">[[Imperial Sourcebook (Second Edition)|''Imperial Sourcebook'', Second Edition]]</ref>

